column2: SELECT mangaID,nsa_z,objra,objdec FROM MYDB.manga_dr1#  OPEN my_cursor   WHILE(#=#)  BEGIN    FETCH NEXT from my_cursor into @mangaID, @nsa_z, @objra, @objdec    IF (@@fetch_status < #) break    INSERT MYDB.MaNGA_specObjID1#    SELECT @mangaID, @nsa_z, s.bestObjID, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid, s.ra, s.dec, s.z, n.distance    FROM dbo.fGetNearestSpecObjEq(@objra,@objdec, #) as n, SpecObj as s    WHERE    n.specObjID = s.specObjID     END         CLOSE my_cursor  DEALLOCATE my_cursor
